My last picture on picplz, from the words of Dolly Parton goodbye, please don't cry, I wish you well, I wish you Love, I love my PicPlz Friends, I will always love you, and many Hugs to All xxxxxxxxxx :-)

I think my pic sharing days end here. I was introduced to Picplz in August and haven't made my goal of 2,000 followers.....but I do appreciate my over 1,900 followers. I still have a lot to learn about photography, and maybe someday I will get that money shot. Thank you for my one BEST OF PICPLZ....that made me hopeful. Thank you to all my followers and friends. I don't think I will continue pic sharing. I thrive on feedback. I don't think I'll find another suitable place for the encouragement that I so greatly need....Good bye friends
